Whaa?
	PHPScripture is a program written to fill a rather obvious (IMHO) need. Basically, this program allows anybody who has a PHP-enabled web server to serve a copy of the Word of God very, very quickly. While the user interface is nice for reading, it's designed expressly for a quick, easy way of sending passages of scripture to and fro, since the scripture reference is actually encoded in the URL, it is easy to send people a link to a passage without typing it in.

